    "fileName": "LarkwellCarePackage",
    "description": "Adds multiple care packages to the orbital workshop for use in the field. Buy the blueprint and the item, add a care package to your pre-mission loadout, then consume it planetside for a hand-picked assortment of gear. No refunds.",
