                    "Description": "NSLOCTEXT(\"D_Itemable\", \"Item_Meta_Carepackage_Fuel-Description\", \"Right click to collect a bundle of two Biofuel canisters, two Oil canisters, and two Hydrazine canisters, all pre-filled and sold at a discount rate.\")",
