                    "Icon": "/Game/Assets/2DArt/UI/Items/Item_Icons/Deployables/ITEM_Meta_Crate_Printed.ITEM_Meta_Crate_Printed",
                    "Description": "NSLOCTEXT(\"D_Itemable\", \"Item_Meta_Carepackage_Oil-Description\", \"Right click to collect a set of basic assets to help jumpstart your oil drilling expedition. Contents include a pair of empty oil barrels, one pumpjack, one crude oil refinery, one natural oil refiner, one oil powered electrical generator, one solar panel, and a set of cables for both oil and electrical connections. All of this comes pre packaged and sold at a discount rate.\")",
